data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Cooley Station community. This stunning home offers a spacious 2,826 sq ft of meticulously designed living space, boasting 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and a convenient 3-car tandem garage. Upon entering, you'll immediately notice the clean and neutral aesthetic that sets the tone for this elegant home. Gray plank tile flooring and soft wall colors create a welcoming and modern atmosphere throughout. The main floor layout features a smart design, with the downstairs primary suite conveniently split from the other bedrooms, offering privacy and comfort. The kitchen is a true focal point of the home, exuding luxury with beautiful upgrades. It showcases a drop-in gas cooktop, Cafe series stainless steel appliances sleek white modern cabinets, granite countertops, a kitchen island complete with a breakfast bar, and a spacious walk-in pantry. The great room is the ideal gathering space, equipped with surround sound featuring 5 speakers, making it perfect for movie nights or entertaining guests. An extended-length center open sliding glass door allows for a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor living. The downstairs primary suite is a haven of relaxation, featuring wood-look floors, a private entrance to the backyard, and a lavish ensuite bathroom. The ensuite boasts a dual sink vanity, a separate soaking bathtub and shower, and a huge walk-in closet, providing ample space and convenience. Heading upstairs, you'll find a spotless loft area with surround sound, 5 speakers and an attached balcony. The remaining bedrooms are immaculate and move-in ready. Plus, a bedroom is downstairs, perfect for a guest room or office! The backyard is designed for easy maintenance, featuring artificial turf and a paved covered patio. This home is a true gem, offering a perfect blend of style, functionality, and comfort. Do not miss your chance! 



Discover an amenity-rich Gilbert, AZ community with sports courts, a resort-style pool, basketball court, and a playground, providing endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation. Plus, enjoy easy access to the freeway for fine dining, entertainment, shopping, and more, making it the perfect place for an active and vibrant lifestyle.
